
A template can take 3 types of parameters:
  
  - type parameters
  - value parameters
  - template parameters

Templates can take a fixed number of parameters or variable parameters if a variadic
template.

Short all cap names are common for template parameters because they have very limited
scope (to that of the template) and it is desirable to avoid name conflicts. Note that
should be wary to avoid conflicts with macro names which tend to be long all cap names.

